    "CMS, 13 13 CMS, 13 CMS, 13 Figure 3:131313133 Figure 3: The measured cross section ratio to Z peak region as a function of DY transverse momentum obtained at √ s = 13 TeV [17] in four mass bins compared with CASCADE3 predictions using three values of q 0: 0.01, 1 and 2 GeV."
